snippet.textDisplay: You know in todays world we are bombarded with different songs, artists, pop, rap, all of it. Yet no one is like Demi. I think that is why as a singer i connect and have actual emotion for her. She is 100% unique in the fact that she is SO DAMN OPEN and has been for the most part since she first went to rehab for her ED. Yet she is SO SO SO underrated in media because of it. Because she is not a perfect princess... because she deson't try and be anything or anyone but herself, she doesn't put ON for the cameras and the fame. Even when she is struggling and trying to hide it she really doesn't.. hide it.. It's so crazy... like every singer today is unique bc every person is unique, but she truly is like no one else in this industry and to imagine losing such a powerhouse HUMAN, not even singer, famous person, but HUMAN in this world makes me so sad and happy that she is slowly starting to come out on the other side of this right now. I think we need to watch her closely bc she is going to be bringing a whole new life to music this year... i can just feel it.
